    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Dei nomine. Die decimo m(ense) madius, inditjone undecima, in <rs
                            key="#Vici">vico</rs> qui vocatur <placeName key="#Vici"
                            ref="#places/3529">Rere</placeName>. <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium"
                            >Breve</rs> recordatjonis ad memoria retinendum de investitjone quas
                        feciit <persName><name ref="Petrus de Azone gastaldo">Petrus de
                            Anzo</name></persName>, pro vice et personas de <persName
                            key="#Viscount"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs> et iussione sua, <rs key="#vassusOf"
                            >vasso</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">misso</rs> de do(mnus) <persName
                            key="#Count"><name ref="Bulgarus">Bullgarus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> de <rs key="#Comitatus">comitato</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/485"><geogName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/2449">Cumiaclienssis</geogName></placeName>. Acedens
                        Petrus de <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Azo"
                                >A[z]o</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldione</rs> supra una <rs
                            key="#Petiae">pecia</rs> terra, ubi abitare visso es <persName
                            key="#Missus #vassusOf"><name ref="Romaldulus"
                            >Romaldellus</name></persName>, in vico qui vocatur Rere et apreendit
                        guazone de terra in manus sua et misit in manibus de Romaldello et dices:
                        ‘Ecce trado adque investio te et per te ad permanendum in te et in
                                <persName><name ref="Eufimia">Ofeia</name></persName> ussori tua et
                        in vestrisque filiis et heredibus in perpetuum’. Et dices Petrus de Azo:
                        ‘Per isto guassone de terra et per issto <rs key="#Cereals">campo</rs> que
                        pertinet ad Albiza investio vobis de onia alia pertinentja sua de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <rs key="#Production">laboratoria</rs> et de <rs key="#Forests">bosscus</rs>
                        adque de <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">padule</rs> adque de onia
                        pertinentja sua que sibi pertinuerit, infra tota <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundoras</rs> vel <rs key="#Fines">territorios</rs>, <rs key="#Plebs"
                            >plebem</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Landed_possessions #Forests #Production #Cereals #Wine #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3650">Sancta Maria in <placeName
                                key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Landed_possessions #Forests #Production #Cereals #Wine #Plebs"
                                ref="#places/3520">Cornacervina</placeName></orgName>, per singulis
                        vel diverssis locis. Que omnia cum terris et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et
                        cum quantascumque a suprascripta res pertinentibus vel supiacentibus que
                        superius legitur que tuum suprascripto Romaldello pertinet per <rs
                            key="#Venditio">conparatjone</rs>’. Et dicens Petrus de Azo. Et insuper
                        inponuit pandum supra ipsa res qualecumque persona ominum umquam in tepore
                        aparuit de suprascripta res intromisserit in contra vestra voluntate aut de
                        vestrisque filiis et heredibus aut desvestire voluerit, sine legale
                        iuditjum, sit composituros et daturos per bandum in cammara do(mnus)
                        Bulgarus sol(idos) <rs key="#Penalty">centum denareis Veronienssis</rs>, et
                        pos bandum solutum, anc remaneat investitjone in sua firmitate. Oc factum es
                        in pre(sencia) Albizo et Petrus igermani et Russticus et Fusscardo filius
                        Bernardus et Bonizo de Iohannes de Fanus et Martinus de Iohannes de Fanus et
                        Petrus nepus de Petrus de Odelardus et aliis plures et mee pre(sente)
                            <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Armatus">Armatus</name></persName>
                        in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio">tabell(io)</rs>. Oc fatum es sup die e
                        mense et inditjone suprascripta undecima, in vico qui vocatur Rere.</ab>
